###############################################################################
#  SPLSD-35 - cereri de test (IntelliJ HTTP Client)
#  Deschide acest fisier in IntelliJ si apasa pe sageata verde din dreptul
#  fiecarei cereri. Presupune ca registrul + cel putin alice/bob/charlie ruleaza.
###############################################################################

### 1. Vezi ce procesoare de flux sunt inregistrate in registru
GET http://localhost:8761/processors

### 2. Identitatea fiecarui procesor (asa cum s-a inregistrat)
GET http://localhost:8081/chat/whoami

### 3. alice difuzeaza un mesaj catre toti ceilalti (coregrafie)
POST http://localhost:8081/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Salut tuturor, sunt alice!"
}

### 4. bob raspunde
POST http://localhost:8082/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Salut alice, aici bob."
}

### 5. Vezi inbox-ul lui bob (ar trebui sa contina mesajul de la alice)
GET http://localhost:8082/chat/inbox

### 6. Vezi inbox-ul lui charlie (mesajele de la alice si bob)
GET http://localhost:8083/chat/inbox

### 7. (optional) sterge manual un procesor din registru dupa id
#   inlocuieste {id} cu un id real obtinut la pasul 1
# DELETE http://localhost:8761/processors/{id}
